(set: _text1 to "Sounds of gunfire woke Bob up. He slowly opened his eyes and tried to remember yesterday. Again he had tried to drown his sorrows in alcohol. This town was not what it used to be. This country was not what it used to be. He threw his blanket aside and stood up. He looked outside through his window from the 76th floor. In the far distance, he recognized several men in black uniforms patrolling.")\
(set: _holder to "Continue...")\
(set: _text2 to "They were Hellsoldiers. Fanatical men and women controlled by Mallory the Hellman. Many of Bob's comrades suspect they are under some kind of hypnosis, but no one knows what is true. It all started 5 years ago at the Jungfernstieg in Hamburg. <br><br> [[Continue...->Intro2]]")\
